<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>ODE Simulation: ΔT & 1000 Cₓ vs t</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background:#fafafa; }
  #app { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
  #controls-container {
    background:#f0f0f0; padding:15px; border:1px solid #ccc; position:relative;
  }
  #controls-container::after{
    content:'+'; position:absolute; top:5px; right:5px; font-size:20px; color:#888;
  }
  .control-row { display:flex; align-items:center; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .control-row label { width:30px; font-weight:bold; margin-right:10px; }
  .control-row input[type="range"]{ flex:1; margin:0 10px; }
  .control-row span { width:80px; text-align:right; font-family:monospace; }
  #plot-container{ width:100%; height:500px; }
</style>
