<title>H₂⁺ Potential Energy and Electron Density</title>
<script src="https://cdn.plot.ly/plotly-latest.min.js"></script>
<style>
  body, html {margin:0;padding:0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden;}
  #app-container {display:flex;flex-direction:column;width:100%;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;}
